{"tid":1388573,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"示威者澄清襲擊警務人員事件","createTime":"2019-07-30T17:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T01:26:50.000Z","uid":12609,"like":242,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"9d20413a463413a0bcdec86c6846edd878d031bf","tid":1388573,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:27:25.000Z","msg":"示威者澄清<br />\n＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n就有報道指有市民於七月三十日晚上在葵涌警署一帶襲擊警務人員。示威者今日（七月三十一日）作出以下澄清：<br />\n<br />\n該名白衣警務人員因天雨路滑不慎滑倒，熱心市民蜂擁上前扶起該名警員，因而引起誤會。<br />\n<br />\n此外，亦有言論指出示威者用雨傘襲擊警員，據消息指只是扶起警員的手臂延伸。<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月31日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間01時25分"},{"pid":"3736a0c5a89338f297279499e90dca53a971457e","tid":1388573,"uid":17232,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:28:00.000Z","msg":"原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真相大白"},{"pid":"746bbebf35709b958f6463a0b16a8f149a28c5f6","tid":1388573,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:28:08.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"f3475082aac4cdfe3d054f698aee5708056a56dc","tid":1388573,"uid":111483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:28:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f6906ad1a2ec36964f97ca0ea0a75e6c682fbc5","tid":1388573,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:28:23.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"76601a99534012a0453fc8dd7a086178815ba6b5","tid":1388573,"uid":17232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:28:38.000Z","msg":"比大家知個真相都係好事"},{"pid":"0f1d3ed4575f86f3936e01d189bf2684b6aa0b21","tid":1388573,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:29:01.000Z","msg":"我睇直播都見到呢個片段"},{"pid":"d117445bbdb64bdfe86772f17fd95babc9a38fdb","tid":1388573,"uid":36158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T17:29:01.000Z","msg":"公道！"},{"pid":"7c310e26ca2b7eb729c14b2d019f2f8b79d6cee3","tid"